### users endpoints

### 3. Hae access_token client_credentials-flowlla
POST https://kubioscloud.auth.eu-west-1.amazoncognito.com/oauth2/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=client_credentials&client_id={{$dotenv KUBIOS_CLIENT_ID}}&client_secret={{$dotenv KUBIOS_CLIENT_SECRET}}

### Get user info by token
GET {{apiurl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Hae käyttäjä ID:llä
GET {{apiurl}}/users/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}



